											&quot;Vampire&quot; squid,
because when it gets protective,
											it pulls this black cape
over its whole body,
											and curls up into a ball.
											Outrageous animal.
											This ship, &quot;The Ship of Dreams&quot; —
											a hundred years ago this coming April,
											this ship was supposed
